Author: TheBlackEyeCam
Text: Oh my god. You room mate could have give a panic attack

Author: thowaway764478
Text: I’ve done this. One time I dreamt I ate a whole box of my roommates twinkies in my sleep in my dream. I woke up panicking and asked my room mate if I ate his food, and he proceeded to tell me yes for the rest of the day and made fun of me for it. Turns out he was joking, and I didn’t do it. But I was so ashamed and panicked so hard.
